Berkshire Hathaway to Invest $5 Billion in Bank of America Amid Share Drop

-- B y   J o A n n e   N o r t o n
-- 
2011-08-25T13:12:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-25/berkshire-hathaway-to-invest-5-billion-in-bank-of-america-amid-share-drop.html
Berkshire Hathaway Inc. (BRK/A)  agreed to
buy 50,000 preferred shares of  Bank of America Corp. (BAC)  for $5
billion, the companies said today in a statement.  Berkshire also will get warrants to purchase 700 million 
common shares.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
JoAnne Norton at 
 jnorton@bloomberg.net  